- Toggle between light and dark mode with a visually appealing switch
- Theme preference is saved in localStorage so it persists between visits
- Respects system preference by default
- Fully responsive design that works on mobile, tablet, and desktop
- Modern UI with subtle animations and hover effects
- Clean, professional aesthetic suitable for a developer portfolio

To view the portfolio, simply open the index.html file in any modern browser. The theme toggle in the top right corner allows switching between light and dark modes.

